{"items":[{"id":"76116","user":{"id":"337130","nickname":"绝命徒神探","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpCHOmz10RBEcUMzkZhHX-o75Upr","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>还有还有，你为啥看到我的教程心里不是滋味？</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1523786710,"created_at":1523786710,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"76115","user":{"id":"337130","nickname":"绝命徒神探","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpCHOmz10RBEcUMzkZhHX-o75Upr","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>再有，推理小说和案件推理是不一样的。现实世界不一定是那个小说里面的世界。不信你去看看《钢穴》，在比对一下现实世界</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1523786526,"created_at":1523786526,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"76114","user":{"id":"337130","nickname":"绝命徒神探","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpCHOmz10RBEcUMzkZhHX-o75Upr","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>现在这个世界就不一样了，以前破案要的就是你的爆炸性思维，现在破案就先用红外线技术照照现场，看看能不能查出指纹来。再开始逻辑推理。</p>\n<p>推理的逻辑有无数种，但是真相只有一个。（看过《推理笔记》和《名侦探柯南》的盆友肯定知道这句话）</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1523786412,"created_at":1523786412,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"76113","user":{"id":"337130","nickname":"绝命徒神探","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpCHOmz10RBEcUMzkZhHX-o75Upr","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>每个人的思维是不一样的，我在那个贴里面嗦了推理的核心是：行为痕迹分析、逻辑学和心理学。</p>\n<p>事实上，推理的逻辑可以演绎为几千种甚至几万种，这就看那个推理者的思维是不是爆炸性的，或者是拘泥于是、墨守成规。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1523786199,"created_at":1523786199,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"76112","user":{"id":"337130","nickname":"绝命徒神探","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpCHOmz10RBEcUMzkZhHX-o75Upr","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>装啥社会人</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1523786062,"created_at":1523786062,"earliest_comments":[]}],"offset":0,"limit":30,"total":5,"counted":true}